items.title: Hero Future Energies to invest Rs 11,000 crore in Karnataka, likely to create 3,000 jobs in renewable energy and green hydrogen
items.description: Hero Future Energies Private Limited (HFEPL)’s proposed projects in Karnataka to invest Rs 11,000 crore over 2-3 years from 2025-26

items.title: JPMorgan drops suit against Tesla over Elon Musk tweet, warrants
items.description: Tesla then filed its own claims that JPMorgan had taken advantage of the tweet to reduce the strike price of more than 1.9 million warrants
